# Output Directory

This directory contains generated results and model outputs:

## Generated Files:
### Model Files:
- `pavement_marking_catboost_model.cbm` - Trained CatBoost model
- `model_performance_metrics.json` - Performance statistics

### Data Processing Results:
- `pavement_marking_data.csv` - Processed dataset for ML
- `pavement_marking_predictions.csv` - Model predictions
- `pavement_marking_projects.csv` - Project-level data
- `bid_tabs_combined.csv` - Combined bid tab data

### Analysis Results:
- `feature_importance.csv` - Feature importance rankings
- `item_error_analysis.csv` - Item-level error analysis  
- `county_statistics.csv` - Geographic analysis
- `work_type_distribution.csv` - Work type breakdown

### Visualizations:
- `actual_vs_predicted.png` - Model performance plot
- `feature_importance.png` - Feature importance chart
- `model_performance.png` - Comprehensive metrics
- `price_trends_by_year.png` - Temporal analysis
- `county_statistics.png` - Geographic visualization
- `item_type_distribution.png` - Item analysis
- `work_type_distribution.png` - Project categorization
- `item_error_analysis.png` - Error analysis

## Usage:
All files in this directory are generated by running the Python scripts.
Run `train_pavement_marking_model.py` to populate this directory with results.

Note: Output files are excluded from the repository due to size but will be generated locally when you run the scripts.
